2011= & \left|\left(\complement_S A_3 \cap \complement_S A_4 \cap \complement_S A_5\right) \cup A_5\right| \\
= & \left|\complement_S A_3 \cap \complement_S A_4 \cap \complement_S A_5\right|+\left|A_5\right| \\
